snippet.title: Cosmo Run (iOS, Android, Amazon, Windows, macOS)
snippet.description:
Cosmo Run is an arcade single and multiplayer game with ever-changing aspect of the play-world. Survive long enough and you will meet special alternative paths - both hardcore and rewarding.

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nosixfive.verto
https://www.facebook.com/nosixfive
